data.description: Newer home in a great location awaits new owner.  Sellers are relocating and hate to leave this adorable home behind.  Well maintained 4 bedrooms with 2 baths and oversized lot is located in one of Robinsons newer neighborhoods.  Granite countertops, stainless appliances, eat in kitchen, LVP floors, and electric fireplace.  Isolated main bedroom has ensuite with separate tub, shower, dual vanities and separate closets.  Close to schools and conveniently located to shopping and eateries.
